cli_content:
Standard IP access list 10
    10 permit 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255
    20 deny any
Extended IP access list 101
    10 permit ip 192.168.1.0 0.0.0.255 10.0.0.0 0.0.0.255
    20 deny icmp any any
    30 permit tcp 192.168.2.0 0.0.0.255 any eq 80
textfsm_template:
Value LIST_NAME (\S+ \S+ \S+ \d+)
Value SEQ_NUM (\d+)
Value ACTION (permit|deny)
Value PROTOCOL (\S+)
Value SRC_ADDR (\S+)
Value SRC_WILDCARD (\S+)
Value DEST_ADDR (\S+)
Value DEST_WILDCARD (\S+)
Value PORT (\S+)

Start
  ^${LIST_NAME}
  ^\s*${SEQ_NUM}\s+${ACTION}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s+${SRC_ADDR}\s+${SRC_WILDCARD}\s+${DEST_ADDR}\s+${DEST_WILDCARD}\s+${PORT}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*${SEQ_NUM}\s+${ACTION}\s+${SRC_ADDR}\s+${SRC_WILDCARD}\s*$$ -> Record
